          1-on-1 Personalised<br/><span class="text-highlight">French Coaching</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
          If you want fast progress and lessons tailored exactly to your needs, my personalised coaching sessions are the perfect choice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5 mb-14" data-stagger>
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-6 text-center reveal">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal/12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">Tailored to You</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/55 text-sm font-light">Sessions customised to your level, learning style and goals</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-6 text-center reveal">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal/12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">50 Min Sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/55 text-sm font-light">Focused one-on-one time for maximum progress</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-6 text-center reveal">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal/12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">Flexible Schedule</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/55 text-sm font-light">Pause or reschedule anytime with 48h notice</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-6 text-center reveal">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal/12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">Certified Teacher</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/55 text-sm font-light">Learn authentic French from a certified teacher</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-stagger>
        <!-- Monthly -->
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-8 reveal flex flex-col" style="border-color: rgba(42,140,130,0.15);">
          <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
            <div class="text-center mb-6 pt-4">
              <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-2">Monthly</p>
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-1 mb-1">
                <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal">360</span>
                <span class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg">$/m</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-charcoal/45 text-sm mb-1">4 sessions per month</p>
              <p class="text-transparent text-sm font-medium select-none" aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1 pl-4">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                50-minute individual sessions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Personalised learning plan
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Cancel anytime &mdash; no commitment
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/28E7sK8kj1PF8QI0cSdIA1H" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">Start Now</a>
            <a href="" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/laprofvirginie/15min?hide_gdpr_banner=1'});return false;" class="block text-center text-charcoal/50 text-sm hover:text-gold-dark transition-colors mt-4 cursor-pointer">
              or book a FREE 15 min call first
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quarterly (Featured) -->
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-8 reveal relative overflow-visible flex flex-col" style="border: 2px solid rgba(42,140,130,0.35);">
          <div class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-5 py-1.5 bg-teal rounded-full z-10 shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-white text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Best Value</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
            <div class="text-center pt-4 mb-6">
              <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-2">Quarterly</p>
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-1 mb-1">
                <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal">320</span>
                <span class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg">$/m</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-charcoal/45 text-sm mb-1">4 sessions per month &mdash; paid quarterly</p>
              <p class="text-gold-dark text-sm font-medium">Save $40/month!</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1 pl-4">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                50-minute individual sessions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Pause classes with 48h notice
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Biggest savings on coaching
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/5kQaEW8kj3XN3wo8JodIA1I" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">Start Now</a>
            <a href="" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/laprofvirginie/15min?hide_gdpr_banner=1'});return false;" class="block text-center text-charcoal/50 text-sm hover:text-gold-dark transition-colors mt-4 cursor-pointer">
              or book a FREE 15 min call first
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <WaveDivider color="#F5F0E8" position="bottom" />
  </section>


  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!-- SECTION 4: ONLINE COURSES                    -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <section class="section-padding relative overflow-hidden bg-cream" id="courses">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-dark font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-3">Online Programs</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">
          Learn at <span class="text-highlight">Your Own Pace</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto font-light">
          Prefer to learn on your schedule? My online courses are designed for busy people who want results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-stagger>
        <!-- French Before You Go -->
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-8 reveal">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-teal/10 text-teal text-xs font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">Mini Course</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">French Before You Go</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/65 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The essentials to get by in France &mdash; from ordering a croissant to impressing your friends and the French! Perfect for travellers.
          </p>
          <a href="/french-before-you-go" class="btn-primary text-sm">
            Learn More
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Master French Grammar -->
        <div class="glass-clear glass-hover p-8 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.15s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-teal/10 text-teal text-xs font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">12-Week Program</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">Master French Grammar &amp; Verbs</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/65 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Say farewell to verb confusion and hello to fluent, effortless expression. A comprehensive 12-week program to transform your French.
          </p>
